{"tid":1030997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加女議員稱中国人「掠食者」 华人團體批種族歧視要求道歉","createTime":"2019-02-21T10:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T14:44:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":73,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"75ece2bd9ef7943b406781d228f5555e8adc5657","tid":1030997,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"加拿大一名議員接受媒體訪問時形容中國人是土地的「掠食者」，被質疑言論涉及種族歧視，引發當地華人抗議，並要求議員道歉。<br />\n<br />\n魁北克省地區議員勒薩爾&middot;特里安近日接受訪問時，形容中國人是土地「掠食者」，「中國人在田間走動，為了未來能佔用它進行準備和宣傳。我們稱他們為『土地掠食者』（land predators），你能看到和感覺到他們。」她強調，「土地一旦賣給中國人，可能永遠不能再為魁北克人提供食物」。<br />\n<br />\n她的言論受到當地華人組織強烈抗議，魁北克「華人進步」組織更批評該言論有種族歧視的嫌疑，著她對所有魁北克華人道歉。不過特里安就回應指自己沒有針對中國人，她表示自己擔心的是來自世界各地的收購者和投資者，並不僅是中國人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1438767/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1438767%2F&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFTWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=d19790c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1438767%2F&h=3a1a6960\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1438767/</a>"},{"pid":"1378e8357c29eea1a44c766220a49c6d342040d5","tid":1030997,"uid":21545,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"事實都歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebb3c403925c207d6032ddf5b43c1fd3fb55175","tid":1030997,"uid":35914,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"用 蝗蟲 就唔會比班畜牲害啦"},{"pid":"4a8aef404d550ae1dba0183e74f51264d813d9d8","tid":1030997,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"HK is not china"},{"pid":"1dcea472f191f38aa5a8b9209097c4141026a900","tid":1030997,"uid":78349,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"1378e8357c29eea1a44c766220a49c6d342040d5","tid":1030997,"uid":21545,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score